,"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40005,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/11\/quran-ikhlaas\/","url_meta":{"origin":15347,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Study the Book for Allah, not the world","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLearn the Quran and use it to ask Allah for Paradise before people learn it to ask for the world. Verily, the Quran is learned for three reasons: a man who uses it to boast,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4469,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/07\/jannah-better-than-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":15347,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Small space in Paradise better than the world","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the small space of a whip in Paradise is better than the entire world and everything in it. Recite the verse if you wish: Whoever is delivered from Hellfire and admitted into Paradise has won.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15347","targetHints":{"allow":["